default6.1
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultBALPA believes that aviation in the North Sea is necessary to ensure a productive oil and gas sector which has huge positive knock-on effects in the local and national economy.  However, our vision is to make every flight a safe flight.
default To improve safety B
defaultALPA makes the following recommendations:
