default6.4
default&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThat frequent and regular reviews of industry best practice be initiated by the CAA in order to keep up with new technology developments, and 
defaultto ensure that all lessons learnt from accidents and AAIB recommendations are universally applied. In particular, new entrants to the market should only have their Operations Manuals approved, when they have been scrutinised to ensure that they incorporate
default all the current industry best practice, rather than 
defaultmere 
defaultcompliance with minimum international standards.
default6.5
